  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765107502\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765107502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765107502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/c08be743a9aecfc31b87051d50ca5256.poster.avif?t=1765107502\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/c08be743a9aecfc31b87051d50ca5256.webm?t=1765107502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/c08be743a9aecfc31b87051d50ca5256.mp4?t=1765107502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Numberline 3 is hard, but very interesting puzzle game, which will force your mind work for all 100%. You have to repeat a mosaic, but it is not very easy. You relax and listen good soundtrack in the beginning and levels are seems to be easy, but after a few levels the game becomes difficult and more exciting! This part of series challange you to deal with hexagons. It gives us a possibility to create much difference in levels for you. Also, clear tutorial await you.<br><br>Game features:<br>- Unique gameplay<br>- Neon design <br>- A large number of levels<br>- Calm music <br>- Simple tutorial",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/c08be743a9aecfc31b87051d50ca5256.poster.avif?t=1765107502\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/c08be743a9aecfc31b87051d50ca5256.webm?t=1765107502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907390/extras/c08be743a9aecfc31b87051d50ca5256.mp4?t=1765107502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Numberline 3 is hard, but very interesting puzzle game, which will force your mind work for all 100%. You have to repeat a mosaic, but it is not very easy. You relax and listen good soundtrack in the beginning and levels are seems to be easy, but after a few levels the game becomes difficult and more exciting! This part of series challange you to deal with hexagons. It gives us a possibility to create much difference in levels for you. Also, clear tutorial await you.<br><br>Game features:<br>- Unique gameplay<br>- Neon design <br>- A large number of levels<br>- Calm music <br>- Simple tutorial",
